📌 Title

Exploring and Visualizing the Iris Dataset

📖 Description

This project focuses on loading, inspecting, and visualizing the famous Iris Dataset to understand patterns, relationships, and distributions in the data.

🎯 Objectives
Load dataset using pandas
Perform basic data inspection
Generate summary statistics
Visualize feature relationships and distributions

🛠️ Tools & Libraries
Python
pandas
matplotlib
Seaborn

